Telkom has launched its Big Deal for April 2018. The latest deal features: Night Surfer data can be used on the Telkom network between midnight and 07:00. Telkom said the Huawei B315 router can connect up to 32 devices at once and features a USB port for connecting hard drives, printers, and other devices. The deal is available until 30 April 2018, and while stocks last. 